{"tid":1824011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美版極醜惡第47集！最新出爐！ 感激12歲美國男孩伊雲仔","createTime":"2020-01-14T06:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T07:31:03.000Z","uid":266362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e4ccd673c88036c60d39348abda4d36b59d3a1ca","tid":1824011,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jVowU2p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjVowU2p.png&h=a1d38119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得響NBA揭幕戰高舉Stand with Hong Kong黑衫支持我地既伊雲仔Matan Even？佢係住美國洛杉磯，宜家就讀七年級。原來響11月開始至今，佢為我地製作<span style=\"color: red;\">多達47條香港警暴極醜惡影片</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好感動！可惜關注度愈來愈低，每條片既<span style=\"color: red;\">觀看次數只有幾百</span>(最初有成幾千)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n大家有時間就上佢TWITTER 同 YOUTUBE CHANNEL 支持下佢luuuu...</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTWITTER: @matanevenoff<br />\nYOUTUBE: Matan Even<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gjRqZx8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgjRqZx8.png&h=a9165373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qpdtcTe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqpdtcTe.png&h=0d7de5a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ThHqe6A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FThHqe6A.png&h=c4650951&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J8bKvEW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ8bKvEW.png&h=e7668a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/doxJMdh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdoxJMdh.png&h=ebb5e248&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eOOtcTi.